      • ccw

        public static double ccw(VPoint p1,
                         VPoint p2,
                         VPoint p3)
        Calculate the counter clockwise result for the three given points.
        ccw(p1,p2,p3) < 0 if p3 is left of Line(p1,p2)
        ccw(p1,p2,p3) = 0 if p3 lies on Line(p1,p2)
        ccw(p1,p2,p3) > 0 if p3 is right of Line(p1,p2)
        Parameters:
        p1 - first point
        p2 - second point
        p3 - third point
        Returns:
        ccw(p1 p2 p3)
